      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TARTAGLIA (1) raced without luck in his two runs back and finds an easier assignment today. Showed good early speed from an outside draw and knocked up late when no match for Koios, finishing sixth over 1250m at Taree. Key jockey change with the tongue-tie going on. Expected to go close in this grade. HERMAN SAID (2) made good improvement last prep and has excellent fresh credentials. Covered plenty of ground in the run when fourth over 1200m at Doomben in C3 grade last March. Wasn't pushed out in his two trials. Will go forward and give plenty of cheek. SENSHI (7) tough gelding who improved sharply when coming out of a decent contest for an eye-catching fourth over 1200m at this track. Gets a good tempo again and has genuine top three prospects. REMEMBER JACK (5) resumes from a lengthy break with a host of gear changes. Disappointed as fav with a fading fifth over 1200m at Canterbury in BM72 class last December. Maps well and sure to be thereabouts.",
